 Galvatron flew acroos the planet surface. He had his fix. He saw them come 
into view. The one he had already taken dna sampale from the other was a new 
one. But contained the skill he needed. He knew the dragon bot would regonize 
him. So it would be easy to lure them away from thier friends.
 Apocalypse glared in disbeilf as the old foe zoomed over his head. He shook 
in fear as he passed. "It cant be....he died.... I killed him.".......
   Death looked at the bot fly over head. He looked at apocalypse and was 
surprised by the fear in his eyes. "Lets get him Death... follow me. Its us 
he is after anyway. He fortold me this when I killed him the first time. This 
time he will stay buried." Apocalypse suddenly took off after it. Death 
immediatly following him but instructed the rest to remain. Whoever that was 
couldnt be that tough........
